column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, s.class ,s.subclass, p.clean dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type p.psfMag_u, p.psfMag_g, p.psfMag_r, p.psfMag_i, p.psfMag_z FROM photoObj p JOIN specObj s ON p.bestobjID = s.objID ORDER BY s.bestobjID where clean=# type=# &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
